<h1> Calculator </h1>
By Kang (Frank) Chen & Matthew Lin <br/>
Type an expression in the following box (e.g., 10.5+20*3/25).

<p>
<form method = "GET">
<input type = "text" name = "expr" />
<input type = "submit" value = "Calculate" />
</form>
